data.description: Looking for a home with an open layout, beautiful views, space to roam AND under $350K?? Then this is the one for you! Come and enjoy country living and lower utility costs in this 1.19 acre lot home w/FULLY OWNED SOLAR and new lower price! Featuring 3BR and 2BA, with the potential for a 4th BR or office, this home offers open living space, vaulted ceilings, a split floor plan and a large back deck with views of Mingus Mountain. There is also a detached 2 car garage, 2500 gal water storage tank and the backyard is fully fenced. Bring the animals and the toys and make this place your home!
